WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.811
<i>- Previously on</i> This Is Us...
- (whispering): Hello?

00:02.835 --> 00:05.053
<i>RON: Hey, Kevin, uh,
it's Ron Howard calling.</i>

00:05.078 --> 00:07.947
Um, I'm prepping a movie
right now that I'm gonna direct.

00:08.164 --> 00:09.381
<i>You would be perfect.</i>

00:10.116 --> 00:11.037
I would?

00:11.062 --> 00:12.117
Can you do that?

00:12.273 --> 00:13.796
- JACK: <i>What are you doing?
- RANDALL: If I can find people</i>

00:13.820 --> 00:15.054
who roll their tongue,

00:15.088 --> 00:16.625
they could be my birth parents.

00:16.656 --> 00:18.296
You know we have
to tell the girls, right?

00:18.726 --> 00:21.529
We're gonna foster a kid, bring
another child into the home.

00:21.554 --> 00:22.953
They need to know about it.

00:22.996 --> 00:25.097
What if we get a kid
that has serious issues

00:25.131 --> 00:27.179
that we're not prepared for?
I'm worried.

00:27.204 --> 00:28.375
I have been drunk

00:29.085 --> 00:30.171
<i>for weeks.</i>

00:30.664 --> 00:32.468
<i>And I need to get a handle on it</i>

00:32.926 --> 00:35.027
<i>before I can walk back into that house.</i>

00:35.052 --> 00:38.688
If you have a problem,
we will fix it together.

00:38.933 --> 00:42.375
You know, you never really talk
about your dad's death.

00:43.016 --> 00:44.210
(crying)

00:44.468 --> 00:46.531
KATE: <i>We-we have to find Kev.</i>

00:46.921 --> 00:48.578
He needs to hear it from me.

00:53.390 --> 00:54.796
JACK: It's been three weeks now.

00:55.450 --> 00:56.679
And, um...

00:57.859 --> 00:59.365
I finally feel like

00:59.773 --> 01:02.429
I'm tackling this thing for real.

01:02.890 --> 01:04.358
So that's good.

01:05.640 --> 01:10.498
I know I'm supposed to talk
more to you guys,

01:10.523 --> 01:14.046
um, really bare my soul.

01:14.750 --> 01:15.968
(laughs softly)

01:16.531 --> 01:19.429
Feels like you get extra
credit around here for...

01:20.014 --> 01:21.335
for crying. (Chuckles)

01:22.416 --> 01:23.554
Um...

01:30.697 --> 01:35.492
I-I promised my wife
that we would talk more,

01:36.036 --> 01:37.039
this time.

01:38.316 --> 01:39.359
But, um...

01:42.542 --> 01:44.312
I'm finding that harder to do.

01:46.079 --> 01:47.093
(insects chirping)

01:51.037 --> 01:52.109
Hmm.

